{"updated_at": {"date": {"d": "10", "m": "06", "Y": "2026"}, "time": {"H": "23", "M": "17", "S": "03"}}, "news": [{"title": "RBI issues final norms on easing bank lending to REITs, InvITs with prudential safeguards", "para": "The Reserve Bank of India has issued final amendments allowing commercial banks to lend to Real Estate Investment Trusts (REITs) and Infrastructure Investment Trusts (InvITs). These directions, incorporating stakeholder feedback, introduce prudential safeguards on exposure limits, asset quality, and repayment structures, while rejecting financing for land acquisition and under-construction assets.", "href": "https://realty.economictimes.indiatimes.com/news/industry/rbi-eases-bank-lending-rules-for-reits-and-invits-with-new-safeguards/131640031?utm_source=newslisting&utm_medium=latestNews", "img": "data:image/png;base64, ", "img-src": "https://etimg.etb2bimg.com/thumb/img-size-69028/131640031.cms?width=150&height=112", "tag": "industry"}, {"title": "DDA auction of 142 properties generates \u20b91,300 crore revenue", "para": "The Delhi Development Authority (DDA) has successfully auctioned 142 properties, generating Rs 1,321 crore in revenue. This mega e-auction saw significant investor participation, realizing nearly three times the cumulative reserve price. The initiative aligns with the Lieutenant Governor's vision for developing Delhi as a global city with sustainable investment and world-class housing.", "href": "https://realty.economictimes.indiatimes.com/news/residential/delhi-dda-generates-1321-crore-revenue-from-auction-of-142-properties/131639891?utm_source=newslisting&utm_medium=latestNews", "img": "data:image/png;base64, ", "img-src": "https://etimg.etb2bimg.com/thumb/img-size-49104/131639891.cms?width=150&height=112", "tag": "residential"}, {"title": "Ranchi civic body intensifies crackdown on illegal buildings over water bodies", "para": "Ranchi Municipal Corporation is intensifying its crackdown on encroachments affecting water bodies and drainage channels. Recent demolitions at Bandhgari and Kanke dam removed illegal structures and piggeries. A comprehensive action plan and special task force are being formed to protect Kanke dam, with surveys also underway along the Harmu river corridor.", "href": "https://realty.economictimes.indiatimes.com/news/infrastructure/ranchi-municipal-corporation-cracks-down-on-illegal-buildings-near-water-bodies/131630884?utm_source=newslisting&utm_medium=latestNews", "img": "data:image/png;base64, ", "img-src": "https://etimg.etb2bimg.com/thumb/img-size-70468/131630884.cms?width=150&height=112", "tag": "infrastructure"}]}